@prefix : <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-market#> .
@prefix bs: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix sec: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-security#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-market>
  a owl:Ontology ;
  owl:imports <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core> ,
              <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-security> ;
  rdfs:label "ByteStar Marketplace" ;
  rdfs:comment "CXP headers, private cells, agora, SHACL+PQC admission gates." .

### Marketplace topology
:PrivateCell a owl:Class .
:Agora a owl:Class .
:Offer a owl:Class .
:Demand a owl:Class .

### CXP headers & admission
:CXPHeader a owl:Class .
:hasHeader a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Offer ; rdfs:range :CXPHeader .
:hasHeader a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Demand ; rdfs:range :CXPHeader .

### Admission predicates
:shapeOk a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :CXPHeader ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:pqcOk a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :CXPHeader ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:congruenceOk a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :CXPHeader ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:admitted a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :CXPHeader ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### Settlement mechanisms
:settlesVia a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :CXPHeader ; rdfs:range sec:KEM .
:privateSettlement a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :CXPHeader ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### Market operations
:matches a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Offer ; rdfs:range :Demand .
:inAgora a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Offer ; rdfs:range :Agora .
:inAgora a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Demand ; rdfs:range :Agora .